snippet.textDisplay:
Two amazing beauty creators, TOGETHER, getting along, and showing support to each other’s latest launches. Now this is a BEAUTIFUL THING. THIS is what gets the beauty industry fired back up again: quality products made right, that are presented as easy to work with but still pro quality! I love TATI and can’t wait to get her new palette and blendiful!! SO flipping excited!!! And now I need to go back into Sephora and find the CT line!!! OMG, I am an OG with both these beautiful ladies!!!

What you both recommend to start with? I’m an experienced MUA but haven’t worked in the industry for a while now. Definitely would love to play with Tati’s new palette and her blediful!! But I also need to get my hands on some of those Charlotte Tilbury products!! The eye liner looks amazing!!! And I’ve been needing a “perk up, if you will. 2020 hasn’t began the best, but that’s OK because it’s still going to be AMAZING!!!!
XOXO’S TO TATI & CHARLOTTE for a fun video and getting the beauty community back to where it should be.
